{"tid":454442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無腸BB堅強活下來　疑威院疏忽　父母不滿院方未交代","createTime":"2017-11-01T06:35:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T08:09:35.000Z","uid":1886,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"fdc21646565334a1ac62505d7d889a2a71fc932d","tid":454442,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:35:06.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】「冇諗過佢可以捱到𠵱家！」出生後5天確診罕見「腸扭結」腸臟幾乎全部壞死，10日內兩度經歷大手術的男嬰浚恒，上周四剛滿4個月大，現時浚恒全部小腸切去，僅餘小部份大腸，男嬰父母驚嘆兒子生命力頑強，但質疑威爾斯親王醫院疏忽在首次開刀手術後未有及時為BB跟進檢查致錯失救治時機，不滿院方至今仍未交代。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171101/large/a0305a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171101%2Flarge%2Fa0305a.gif&h=adb7452b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">長有一雙大眼睛的浚恒，現靠注射營養液維持生命。</span><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171101/20200851\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171101%2F20200851&d=NvoLAQrF2iDzGXEcyQKP6o9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=2c6178b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171101%2F20200851&h=ec660caf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171101/20200851</a></div>"},{"pid":"b7bb614c822fa7c3fa6626b8d191493651500e5a","tid":454442,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:37:15.000Z","msg":"生於6月26日的浚恒長有一雙大眼睛，看見父母會手舞足蹈「咯咯」笑，由於腸道不全無法進食，現時他每日須進行20小時靜脈注射營養液維持生命，爸爸邱生回憶當初兒子拔喉後與死神搏鬥，肚皮三度開刀留下蜈蚣般恐怖疤痕，他語帶哽咽說兒子活下來有如奇蹟。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171101/large/01la3p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171101%2Flarge%2F01la3p3.jpg&h=ca062783&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">浚恒父親不時翻看手機內兒子的照片，盼浚恒戰勝病魔，健康成長。</span></div>"},{"pid":"39aa8da8fde0143bace87051d633fa25be6ee8ca","tid":454442,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:38:43.000Z","msg":"浚恒較預產期早半個月出生，體重僅得2.38公斤，分娩期間母子發高燒，出生第5日他因腹脹開刀揭發腸扭結，小腸呈360度扭結致阻塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，胃部亦谷爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，醫生曾動手術扭正小腸，但10日後再開刀發現小腸全部壞死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，當時醫生亦打定輸數拔走氣喉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但他卻活下來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，並於8月初接受第3次手術切除全部小腸及大部份大腸。威院事後曾回應稱已盡力治療，並在6月30日嬰兒嘔吐及腹脹後做手術。<br />\n<br />\n精靈愛笑的浚恒現時重3.8公斤雖較同齡嬰兒小，但爸媽希望他可於聖誕節前長至5公斤，屆時便可達到出院要求回家一起慶祝聖誕節，邱先生指若一切如願，今年Boxing Day就是在家中慶祝浚恒半歲生日，並完成帶兒子看大海的願望。"},{"pid":"2b270112a766d1847d676cdb83a078dc26a90c39","tid":454442,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ceba2b8bbe4b8bc066ca9c0b602205ce0c816d9","tid":454442,"uid":152408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:45:37.000Z","msg":"痛死"},{"pid":"f4c542b2961287c8ee1d996ee544fba3fca3286d","tid":454442,"uid":117628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:46:52.000Z","msg":"大個左唔知點食野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"633abf7d08e0b2ad67175b5cd146117aeb895384","tid":454442,"uid":139815,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:49:00.000Z","msg":"個BB有點兒像C君"},{"pid":"dd96ac3aa68793ea13334e51fe8ff8c4fc7ba9a0","tid":454442,"uid":38523,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:51:24.000Z","msg":"政府反正有班保皇狗護住<br